Published 2:09 am Friday, August 2, 2024

The San Jose State Spartans are +6000 to win the MWC in 2024, as they have the 10th-ranked odds in the conference. We have more details on futures odds, along with the important stats you need to know, in the article below.

San Jose State Mountain West Conference and National Championship Odds

National Championship Odds: Currently Unavailable

Mountain West Conference Championship Odds: +6000 (Bet $10 to win $600.00)

Season Win Total Over/Under: 4.5 (Bet $10 to win $10.50 on the over with +105 odds)

Bet on San Jose State Spartans futures odds & games on BetMGM.

San Jose State 2024 Schedule

San Jose State has been given the 93rd-ranked schedule this season (based on its opponents’ combined win total last year). The Spartans will take on six teams this season that went over .500 in 2023. That schedule will pair them against one team that ended with nine or more victories and three squads with fewer than four wins last season.
